```BASIC RULES```
**. Your character's name must be the same as steam profile and discord**

· **OOC** (Out of character) : Lezmek dima to93od in character fi west l game w ma tahkich hrp ( ned3i / khalal / 7al 3inaya / machhed / 3asfor /tatbi9 / bech nemchi 3omra etc.. )

· **RDM** (Random death match) : Mamnou3 to9tel wala tadhreb player men ghir reason

· **VDM** (Vehicle death match) : Mamnou3 testa3mel vehicle bech to9tel wala tadhreb player

· **Fail Drive**: Mamno3 tamel hajet b vehicle ma tnajamch tamalhom fedenia (on road vehicle temchi biha off road - tsou9 b3ajla man9ouba - tnaggez min blassa 3alya)

·** Clear Shot** : Mamno3 toktel walla tadhreb player andou rahina 

· **Pain RP** : Ki tetdhrab wala ta3mel accident wala 3amaliya lezmek tetwaja3 w tetasarref kima IRL

· **VOL** (Value of life) : Mamnou3 tamel haja tkhali hyet character mteek fi risque (Prison fih Vol & Police Taser fih Vol kif tkoun we9ef w distance binetkom 9riba w 7at 3lik aim & if your vehicle was blocked that you can not move forward  or backward and there is melees on you you need to surrender = vol)

· **Power Gaming** Ma tet9awech 3al character mteek w tamel hajet maysiroch IRL (exp ta3mal 3amaliya walla accidon w t9oum tejri direct)

· **Meta Gaming** : Mamno3 testa3mel info makech makhedhha RP w Mamnou tet3arraf 3la player lebes mask except player fi nafs ilfaction mte3ek (matnejjem tet3arraf 3la player ken matchouf wejhou walla lbes mask 9oddemek + ilmask w clothes color repair lil gangs walla factions only)

· **Fail RP** : Mamno3 taamel hajet mouch logique w maysirouch IRL 

· **Coherence RP** : Mamno3 ta3mel des actions ma yetmachewech maa l'character type mteek walla ykoun esmek mouch coherant m3al faction mte3ek walla telbes mask wala clothing color mta3 other factions or gangs..

· **Force RP** : Mamno3 tet9awa 3la player/tforci alih  bech terbah scene (exp ta5taf hostage w tofroth 3la s7abou bech yjiw tfightihom)

· **Win RP** : Mamno3 takhle9 7ajet moch mawjoudin in game bech terba7 bihom scene

· **Combat Logging** : Mamnou3 tab9a AFK walla ta3mal ALT-F4 fi west scene

· **Combat Storing** : Mamnou3 tohreb l blassa t5allich 8irek ykammal maak scene walla t5arraj item walla vehicle m scene  (Ex:  tahrab l safe zone / house / garage / stache.. ) walla tahreb fi pursuit t5abbi items w t3awed terja3 l scene tmanna3 s7abek)

· **Use Rule** : Mamnou3 testa3mel rule bech tcouvri beha rou7ek wala terba7 beha scene ( Ex: teprovoqui abed fi safe zone khatr ta3ref ma ynejjem yamalek chy )

· **1 Day Reaction** : ki tmout fi fight ma 3andekch el 7a9 tarja3 trevengi fi nafs nhar w no reaction after 7 days (new day start at 20h00) (exp 9talt player 19h00 ynejjem yreacti 3lik ba3d 20h00)

· **Wrong use of /do & /me** :  /do actions  /me  feelings & expression (exp /me hahah walla ta3ti infos walla question = ban)

· **No Fake hostages** :  Mamno3 alik thez sahbek walla player mitfehem m3ah rahina

· **Safe Zones** : Hospital - Apartement - Police department - Sheriff department + events + central bank + cinema + casino + restaurants + mall (tnejjemch telbes mask walla teprovoqui walla tejbed weapons walla ta3mal illegal deals or scam in safe zone)

· **Spam punch interdit ** (tnejjemch tab9a tespami bil box)

· **No Poor quality roleplay** lezem tkoun fairplayer w characterek ykoun coherant m3al backstory w trespcti elli tsceni m3ah w mat7awelch terba7 scene b ay tari9a walla tebda teprovoqui players for fun walla bech tjib reason mta3 fight walla braquage) 

· **Troll interdit** (ma3andekch il7a9 tetrolli b façon 5ayba 3la player ma ya3rfekch walla tab9a tfarrek fiha 3al players w tfassad l'enviromnnement roleplay mta3 8irek fi serveur)

· **Fights with Zero interaction is porhibited only in reactions you don't need it** ( w ken bech tsir provaction par tel lezem twadha7lou elli enti bech tfightih)

·** You can not loot food & drinks & lockpick & pd stuff & identity card & driver liscence, all the rest is allowed to loot **


